title: Nine To Noon - 3/1 Nordo in for PA... Michelletti, Gaard, Lavelle join!
description: Nordo in the big chair today filling in for PA... Pat Micheletti joins Nordo in studio to talk about the state of the State of Hockey including the red-hot MN Wild! Justin Gaard joins to discuss what has gone wrong in DinkyTown in regards to men's hoops... and Lavelle checks in from sunny Florida to talk Twins from Fort Meyers! Plus an impromptu call to Russo Radio to talk about Alex Stalock's time in MN coming to an end.
